e in situ measurements of a very low\ndensity ahead of the shock at STEREO A.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Nov 2016 03:23:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Jan 2017 02:51:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-19"}
