up to (almost) two\norders of magnitude, and this conclusion is consistent with the one observed\nearlier for Be-like ions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Nov 2016 12:33:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-16"}
